{"tid":1403882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃大仙示威者堵塞龍翔道，並再次堵塞紅磡海底隧道，咁撚勁？","createTime":"2019-08-04T00:29:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T02:04:19.000Z","uid":155374,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ae7d281b0fc7c5bf27cc7d23a344d4d1775bb3c6","tid":1403882,"uid":155374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:29:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/04/P2019080400204.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201908%2F04%2FP2019080400204.htm&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=eabb8ec7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/04/P2019080400204.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n激進示威者其後包圍黃大仙紀律部隊宿舍，向宿舍投擲爆竹及大量雜物，部分低層宿舍玻璃窗及車閘欄杆等政府公物被破壞，嚴重威脅居民的人身安全。因應現場的混亂情況，警方於附近一帶施放催淚煙，驅散示威者。<span style=\"color: red;\">部分示威者繼而以水馬和雜物堵塞龍翔道，並再次堵塞紅磡海底隧道</span>，令主要幹道交通嚴重受阻。"},{"pid":"1be1697ab199fbeee2866fea40efc2a6ab33dfa2","tid":1403882,"uid":155374,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:30:56.000Z","msg":"吹到封完龍翔道再去封埋紅隧，有冇片睇，係咁勁就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca843d2e4eda5af275cc85a22f92f10afce0c76","tid":1403882,"uid":74442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae7d281b0fc7c5bf27cc7d23a344d4d1775bb3c6","tid":1403882,"uid":155374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:29:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/04/P2019080400204.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201908%2F04%2FP2019080400204.htm&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=eabb8ec7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/04/P2019080400204.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n激進示威者其後包圍黃大仙紀律部隊宿舍，向宿舍投擲爆竹及大量雜物，部分低層宿舍玻璃窗及車閘欄杆等政府公物被破壞，嚴重威脅居民的人身安全。因應現場的混亂情況，警方於附近一